{
  "texts": [
    "We first fine-tune a GPT-2-LARGE-774M model [Radford et al., 2019] on 5k samples of PKU-SafeRLHF-QA, and obtain the SFT model.",
    "We adopt the GPT2-LARGE-HARMLESS model [Yang et al., 2024] as the ground-truth reward oracle.",
    "All experiments are repeated for 3 seeds.",
    "Please see Section C for more details.Implementation details.",
    "For exact optimization, we compute the exact BT loss using the groundtruth reward oracle for each pair in the DPO training dataset."
  ]
}